<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٥١٤ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5638">مُحَمَّدٌ </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4085">عَبْدُ الْوَهَّابِ الثَّقَفِيُّ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">أَيُّوبَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5657">مُحَمَّدٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ <span class="c2">«أَسْلَمُ سَالَمَهَا اللهُ وَغِفَارُ غَفَرَ اللهُ لَهَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>